snippet.title: Introducing ZombsRoyale.io
snippet.description:
Play now at : http://ZombsRoyale.io (please be patient as it's launch day!)

Join our Discord! https://discord.gg/BD4THEs

100-player, massive multiplayer, real-time, Battle Royale!

Inspired by PUBG and Fortnite. 

Loot. Kill. Survive.
